& SUSE SLES15 SP3 based out of QAT2.0 OOT driver

Clean up clang scan build warning with redundant variable assignment

The variable priv_key is being assigned but it is never used later. The
variable and assignment are redundant and can be removed. Cleans up
clang scan build warning:

qat_hw_ec.c:716:26: warning: Although the value stored to 'priv_key' is
used in the enclosing expression, the value is never actually read
from 'priv_key' [deadcode.DeadStores]
    if (ecdh == NULL || (priv_key = EC_KEY_get0_private_key(ecdh)) == NULL) {
